data.Name: WhoHurtYou
data.Bio: WhoHurtYou is an American darkpop project formed by All Time Low guitarist Jack Barakat and Kevin Fisher, signed to Fueled by Ramen. They started releasing singles in 2019, before releasing their EP, "Stages" on 1 November 2019. Since then, they have released another single, "The One That Got Away". Read more on Last.fm
